OUT HERE FOR THANKSGIVING.

00:31.765 --> 00:33.167
YEAH, MY MOTHER'S EXPECTING US.

00:33.201 --> 00:35.169
MY SISTER'S FLYING UP
FROM MIAMI.

00:35.203 --> 00:38.339
NO, LOOK, THIS ISN'T
UP FOR DISCUSSION, ALL RIGHT?

00:38.372 --> 00:39.573
NO--WELL, YEAH, WHO'S YELLING?

00:39.607 --> 00:41.242
I'M NOT YELLING.

00:41.275 --> 00:43.377
NO, YOU DON'T HANG--
DON'T HANG UP ON ME.

00:43.411 --> 00:44.412
MARIA?

00:45.446 --> 00:47.348
DAMN IT.

00:47.381 --> 00:49.350
- WHOA.

00:49.383 --> 00:52.353
HEY, YOU ALL RIGHT?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

00:52.386 --> 00:54.622
- NOTHING.

00:54.655 --> 00:56.657
- OKAY, TAKE A BREATH.

00:56.690 --> 00:59.660
- HOW ABOUT YOU DON'T TELL ME
WHAT TO DO?

01:06.700 --> 01:08.702
- DON'T SAY IT.

01:08.736 --> 01:10.238
- SAY WHAT?

01:12.140 --> 01:14.108
- HEY, WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR HAND?

01:14.142 --> 01:16.076
- AH, NOTHING; IT'S FINE.

01:20.414 --> 01:21.782
- THAT WORK-RELATED?

01:21.815 --> 01:23.584
- YEAH, SOME GEEK HACKED

01:23.617 --> 01:26.420
