IN THE PICS ARE UNDERAGE.

01:31.825 --> 01:33.327
THAT MAKES IT CHILD PORN.

01:33.361 --> 01:34.628
- OKAY, WRAP IT UP, FIN.

01:34.662 --> 01:36.630
FIND ANYTHING,
HAVE TARU TRACE IT.

01:36.664 --> 01:38.766
- YOU KNOW YOU DON'T WANT
NAKED PICTURES OF YOURSELF

01:38.799 --> 01:40.134
ON THE INTERNET,

01:40.168 --> 01:41.502
