THE BLACK AND WHITE GALA

02:28.449 --> 02:30.384
AT THE MET SIX WEEKS AGO.

02:30.418 --> 02:32.553
TONS OF PRESS COVERAGE.

02:34.855 --> 02:36.290
- I DON'T REMEMBER
HEARING ANYTHING

02:36.324 --> 02:38.392
ABOUT A.J. MARTIN BEING
PICKED UP ON A DOMESTIC.

02:38.426 --> 02:39.627
- WELL, THEY MUST HAVE
PICKED HIM UP,

02:39.660 --> 02:41.929
BECAUSE A PATROLMAN SHOWS UP.

02:41.962 --> 02:43.197
- THE GUY'S A SPORTS HERO.

02:43.231 --> 02:44.398
YOU KNOW HOW THIS GOES.

02:44.432 --> 02:45.833
- WELL, I KNOW HOW
IT USED TO GO.

02:45.866 --> 02:48.869
