SHE CAN HARDLY WALK.

02:48.902 --> 02:52.373
FIND OUT IF THERE'S ANY VIDEO
OF WHAT HAPPENED IN BETWEEN.

02:52.406 --> 02:53.707
- YEAH, I DON'T SEE IT
POSTED ANYWHERE.

02:53.741 --> 02:54.875
WE CAN CONTACT THE GARAGE.

02:54.908 --> 02:56.244
- YOU KNOW, CALL THE LOCAL
PRECINCT.

02:56.277 --> 02:57.445
FIND OUT WHAT REALLY HAPPENED.

02:57.478 --> 02:58.446
I'LL CALL THE CHIEF.

02:58.479 --> 02:59.880
- YOU WANT US TO INVESTIGATE?

02:59.913 --> 03:02.283
- AFTER RAY RICE AND THE OTHERS,

03:02.316 --> 03:03.717
