04:00.774 --> 04:03.577
- WELL...THAT'S HOW.

04:03.611 --> 04:05.779
SEXUAL ASSAULT.

04:05.813 --> 04:08.682
- MUST BE SLOW DOWNTOWN.

04:08.716 --> 04:10.484
