AT THE SCENE.

04:12.586 --> 04:14.355
- YEAH, WE SAW THAT,
BUT SHE WAS WOOZY,

04:14.388 --> 04:17.458
SHE'S MISSING A SHOE,
SHE LOOKED ROUGHED UP.

04:17.491 --> 04:20.861
- MS. BRYANT DECLINED
MEDICAL ATTENTION.

04:20.894 --> 04:22.062
HE WAS POLITE.

04:22.095 --> 04:23.797
SHE WAS CONTRITE.

04:23.831 --> 04:25.666
