WERE CONSISTENT?

04:25.699 --> 04:27.535
- IT WAS MORE OF A DISCUSSION.

04:27.568 --> 04:29.937
- BUT THEY WERE
SPOKEN TO SEPARATELY?

04:29.970 --> 04:32.306
- I DIDN'T SEE THE NEED.

04:32.340 --> 04:35.443
LOOK, WE GOT A LOT OF SWELLS
UP HERE,

04:35.476 --> 04:37.478
