THREW THE BOOK AT HIM

05:19.920 --> 05:20.888
IS AN OVERSTATEMENT.

05:20.921 --> 05:23.023
- THE PRECINCT COPS SAID
IT WAS A DRUNKEN SPAT.

05:23.056 --> 05:25.426
