AGAINST PAULA,

05:25.459 --> 05:27.728
OFFERED A.J. ADJOURNMENT
IN CONTEMPLATION OF DISMISSAL.

05:27.761 --> 05:29.630
HE DOES COMMUNITY SERVICE,
DIDN'T RE-OFFEND--

05:29.663 --> 05:31.832
- IN SIX MONTHS,
IT ALL GETS DROPPED.

05:31.865 --> 05:32.966
- LOOK, THAT'S THE DEAL
THAT I GIVE

05:33.000 --> 05:34.001
WHEN THE VICTIM REFUSES
TO COOPERATE.

05:34.034 --> 05:36.036
OR ARE YOU SAYING
BECAUSE THEY'RE CELEBRITIES,

05:36.069 --> 05:38.105
WE SHOULD HAVE GIVEN THEM
ANTI-PREFERENTIAL TREATMENT?

05:38.138 --> 05:39.206
- I'M SAYING THAT YOUR A.D.A.

05:39.239 --> 05:41.675
SHOULDN'T HAVE TAKEN
THE ARRESTING OFFICER'S WORD.

05:41.709 --> 05:43.377
- I TAKE YOUR WORD ALL THE TIME.

05:43.411 --> 05:45.379
ANYWAY, THIS IS MOOT.

05:45.413 --> 05:47.114
THE DEAL WAS OFFERED;
THE LAWYER SAID NO.

05:47.147 --> 05:49.683
- THEY TURNED DOWN
A "GET OUT OF JAIL FREE" CARD?

05:49.717 --> 05:51.919
WHY?
- IT'S THE SMART MOVE.

05:51.952 --> 05:54.087
A.J. CALLED THE A.D.A.'S BLUFF.

05:54.121 --> 05:56.857
HE JUST ASSUMED THAT HE'D
GET AWAY WITH IT REGARDLESS.

05:56.890 --> 05:59.026
WHAT, HE'S PROBABLY
WORRIED ABOUT P.R.,

05:59.059 --> 06:00.661
