WITH EVERYTHING.

06:02.830 --> 06:04.998
- EVERYTHING?
LOOK, THERE'S NOT A LOT HERE.

06:05.032 --> 06:06.534
ANY FOOTAGE FROM THE STAIRWELL?

06:06.567 --> 06:08.636
- AMARO AND ROLLINS
ARE TRACKING IT DOWN.

06:08.669 --> 06:10.103
- AND WHEN THEY FIND IT,

06:10.137 --> 06:11.905
