SHE SLIPPED AND FELL?

06:23.216 --> 06:24.518
COME ON.

06:24.552 --> 06:25.318
- IN CERTAIN WAYS,
I DON'T DISAGREE.

06:25.352 --> 06:26.620
- I HATE IT WHEN PEOPLE
SAY THAT.

06:26.654 --> 06:27.821
- SINCE HE DIDN'T
TAKE THE OFFER,

06:27.855 --> 06:28.822
THE CASE IS STILL OPEN.

06:28.856 --> 06:31.024
FIND THE VIDEO,
OR GET HER TO CHANGE HER STORY.

06:31.058 --> 06:32.893
