A CONDITIONAL DISCHARGE.

06:40.167 --> 06:41.602
MY LEGAL TEAM'S ON IT.

06:41.635 --> 06:43.537
- THAT WAS BEFORE
THE VIDEO CAME TO LIGHT.

06:43.571 --> 06:44.805
- YEAH, WELL, I MEAN,

06:44.838 --> 06:46.507
THAT'S WHAT YOU SHOULD
BE FOLLOWING UP ON.

06:46.540 --> 06:48.041
