06:48.075 --> 06:51.645
- WE HAVE DETECTIVES
WORKING ON THAT.

06:51.679 --> 06:52.846
- GOOD THROW, SHORTY.

06:52.880 --> 06:54.081
- I'M GONNA BE A PLAYER,
JUST LIKE MY DAD.

06:54.114 --> 06:55.516
