THE RESTROOM, PLEASE?

07:33.186 --> 07:36.056
- YEAH, SURE,
IT'S RIGHT DOWN HERE.

07:36.089 --> 07:37.858
- THANKS.
- HAVE A SEAT.

07:42.663 --> 07:45.098
- YOU KNOW WHAT THIS
IS ALL ABOUT, RIGHT?

07:45.132 --> 07:47.501
- YEAH.
YOU GOT TO DO YOUR JOB.

07:47.535 --> 07:48.936
I RESPECT THAT.

07:48.969 --> 07:51.138
- ALL THE ATHLETES
IN THE PRESS RIGHT NOW--

07:51.171 --> 07:54.207
