TO TELL ME ABOUT THAT NIGHT,

08:27.875 --> 08:30.143
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED?

08:30.177 --> 08:32.179
- NO, I'D BEEN DRINKING.

08:32.212 --> 08:34.214
