CULTURAL EXEMPTIONS?

09:41.248 --> 09:43.984
- YOU KNOW, MY FATHER,
HE WENT AT ME WITH HIS FISTS.

09:44.017 --> 09:46.687
IT TAUGHT ME YOU NEVER LAY
A HAND ON A CHILD,

09:46.720 --> 09:48.021
OR A WOMAN.

09:48.055 --> 09:49.356
- IT'S POSSIBLE THAT A.J.

09:49.389 --> 09:51.759
COULD HAVE BEEN FENDING HER OFF.

09:51.792 --> 09:53.160
- FENDING HER OFF?
[cell phone rings]

09:53.193 --> 09:55.829
